                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            Ride or Die                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘The first rule of this friendship is that it is devoted, overly so, as intrinsic and codependent and borderline morbid as any ill-fated romance.’<br><br>

Megan Nolan on intense friendships.                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
